# This is a PC building website

1.  PC build tool is protected, user cannot open the tool without login
2.  If you want to know the details of a product, click on the name of the product and you will see the details of that product

3.  With PC Build Tools, the user can build with the components of their choice with PC Build Tools.
1.  Going into the build tool will show some component categories
2.  Click the Choose button on the right side to see the single component
3.  Clicking the Add button will add a component
4.  When the requirement components are selected then the complete button will show, if you click the complete button and show success then your work is done.
